---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="Ramjan Khandelwal — computer science student, writer, tinkerer." activeNav="about">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Hey, I'm Ramjan. I'm a computer science student at VIT Chennai, working my way
        through AI, robotics, and the messy beauty of programming. Most of my time goes
        into building things for the web — sometimes they work smoothly, sometimes they
        break in ways that teach me more than tutorials ever could.
      </p>
      <hr />
      <p>
        I enjoy tinkering with React, Next.js, databases, and occasionally going down
        rabbit holes with machine learning and Linux.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of code, I play guitar, write when I can, and keep a curious eye on how
        people think and behave. Those things keep me grounded when the tech side of
        life gets too loud.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can find my projects on <a href="https://github.com/ravenZ3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>,
        or drop me a note at <a href="mailto:ramjankhandelwal7@gmail.com">ramjankhandelwal7@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>This garden</h2>
      <p>
        This is a digital garden — not a blog. Notes here are organized by type and growth
        stage, not date. A seedling is a rough idea; a budding note is developing; an
        evergreen note is polished and maintained. Notes link to each other; backlinks appear
        automatically.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-header { padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>
